  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_ingot.tooltip1": "一种沉重的宇宙合金。",
  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_ingot.tooltip2": "用它锻造的工具极其坚固，",
  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_ingot.tooltip3": "绝不容忍脆弱的木质。",
  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_nugget.tooltip1": "一块坚固的钢之碎片。",
  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_nugget.tooltip2": "完全足以用作",
  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_nugget.tooltip3": "牢固的金属手柄。",
  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_shield.tooltip1": "专为抵御恒星风暴而造。",
  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_shield.tooltip2": "它的坚韧让凡俗的盾牌",
  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_shield.tooltip3": "显得如同脆弱的玩具。",
  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_helmet.tooltip1": "当穿戴全套装备时，你将无视重力法则。",
  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_helmet.tooltip2": "你的步伐变得沉重，",
  "item.skystone.meteorite_iron_helmet.tooltip3": "但深渊不再能对你造成伤害。",
